    public interface ImplicitDepsInferringDescription<T>
    While building up the target graph, we infer the implicit dependencies of a rule by parsing all parameters with types SourcePath or BuildRule. However, in some cases like GenruleDescription, the AbstractGenruleDescription.CommonArg.getCmd() argument contains build targets in a specific format. Any Description that implements this interface can modify its implicit deps by poking at the raw build rule params.
